categories: Category:Unidentified Jedi of the Jedi Order

nodes.text: A female Jedi served as Supreme Commander of all Jedi forces on the planet Corellia during the Battle of Corellia between the Galactic Republic and the Sith Empire in 3640 BBY. The Jedi fought alongside the Republic Military in defense of Corellia, though she was killed, and the Sullustan Jedi Nae Nuuv claimed that her body had been vaporized during the fighting. The Jedi was succeeded as Supreme Commander by the Jedi Knight known as the Hero of Tython.

The unidentified Jedi commander was first mentioned in the Jedi Knight class mission "Jedi Commander" in Star Wars: The Old Republic, a video game released by BioWare and LucasArts. The Jedi's name and species were not identified.
